<div class="row">
    <h1 class="col-xs-12">Let me help you to find an accommodation or a roommate!</h1>
    <p class="col-xs-12"><strong>This web service is totally free of charges!</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Looking for somebody?</h2>
                <p>Use the field below to search for an user.<br />
                <em>Note that you must be registered to display the users' profile.</em></p>
                <form>
                    <label for="user_tokens">User's name:</label>
                    <input type="text" name="user_tokens" id="user_tokens" >
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>Is it you first visit?</h2>
                <p>
                    You can start by looking over the adverts or you can also search for your fiends or for properties.<br />
                    In order to display users' profile or the details of a property, you must be registered. <%= link_to 'Create my account now!', new_user_path %>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Our properties</h2>
        <%= image_tag "https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?size=450x300"+@markers %>
    </div>
</div>
